<h1><em>quantifier</em> @HI{{ha}}</h1>

<h2> Formation </h2>

<p>
<ol>
<li> <strong><em>quantifier</em> @HI{{ha}}</strong>
</ol>
</p>

<h2> Definition </h2>

When it follows a quantifier, the particle @HI{{ha}} indicates that the speaker believes
this to be the minimum amount necessary.
<p></p>

<h2> Examples </h2>

<ol>
<li>
<table class="sentence">
