      200@KJ{{ten*thousand}}<strong>@KJ{{circle}}@HI{{ha}}</strong> @KJ{{need}}@HI{{rimasu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      In Japan you need at least 2 million yen to hold a wedding.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</ol>

